ActFederal Real Property Act
SubjectSettlement and Release Agreement Canada-Alberta
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Natural Resources to enter into the SETTLEMENT AND RELEASE AGREEMENT between Her Majesty in right of Canada and Her Majesty in right of Alberta to settle a constitutional dispute concerning ownership over certain mines and minerals and situated within Alberta but held by Canada, and to obtain a release in relation thereto. The order also enables the Minister to make the settlement payment provided for in the agreement to Alberta.
